Author: BabyBaphomet_
Text: Nah thats just feeling sick and puking. Don't worry about it, it's probably just a one-off thing! If it keeps happening though definitely see a doctor.

Author: clownboyvibes
Text: No, you can not unintentionally purge. Purging is *purposefully* doing things to make up for the food you ate in order to not gain weight, whether that be throwing up or whatever. "Unintentionally purging" is just regular vomiting. You should be fine. Hope you feel better soon!
